After the configuration is deployed, a synchronization in **AgroCD** is necessary. AgroCD can be accessed through the Command Center home page by clicking the AgroCD icon in the overview table.

![A screenshot of a computer  Description automatically generated](data:image/png;base64,)

An ArgoCD interface opens. Click on the **Sync** button to synchronize the changes. This opens a pop-up window for synchronization settings.

> Note

It is recommended to select the **Prune** checkbox before clicking **Synchronize**. This will delete any older configurations.
